columns.comment: The tables show the conditions on December 31st for each respective year according to administrative subdivisions of January 1st of the following year
Population growth is defined as the difference between the population at the beginning of the year and at the end of the year.

comments.comment: Since 1 January 2003, a new regional division has been established. Parts of Uppsala municipality have formed a new municipality called Knivsta.
